e":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T02:38:19.000Z","msg":"潑冷水？長西方志氣滅自己威風？"},{"pid":"505ad1048290228dc25b91f940a84dd934b47dd4","tid":2383382,"uid":355748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T03:01:43.000Z","msg":"呢排樓市跌咗dd 開始發羊吊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed48ef404fe72833f2291c8fc2d86354710026d8","tid":2383382,"uid":67896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T03:13:51.000Z","msg":"咁仲慶唔慶祝聖誕節<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b9f64dfd121da894a1d9063dd29885712b0adef","tid":2383382,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T08:10:21.000Z","msg":"教習近平屌閪你傻架？"},{"pid":"8e0b8c6f924390754a452a115998f0a144cac9ed","tid":2383382,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T09:57:08.000Z","msg":"漢奸"},{"pid":"a40cd0f5d5397fb2009450e86a0b9345336722cd","tid":2383382,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T09:59:43.000Z","msg":"妄議中央"}],"pinned":{"pid":"7bb463db800583426780eabde7e5d61bc345a788","tid":2383382,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T02:05:17.000Z","msg":"重用聖誕卡算唔算敵視西方文明?"}}